CatDescriptText: Headline for related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "Out-of-Towners Enjoy Frogs' Swank Formal in Pittsburgh Room of Penn-Sheraton Hotel"
TitMainTitle: Men, including Rev. LeRoy Patrick wearing eyeglasses and dark jacket on left, and women, wearing light colored gown with ruffles, dancing in couples in  Pittsburgh Room of Penn Sheraton Hotel for FROGS formal
